snippet.title: Medieval Kingdom Wars - Alpha Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: First video gameplay presentation for Reverie World Studio`s upcoming Grand Strategy game - Medieval Kingdom Wars. This is pre-alpha footage of an early game build. Footage is 100% filmed in-game. Visual and game quality willy improve over the development cycle.
